[
  "Manfredi Lefebvre d'Ovidio is the executive chairman of Silversea Cruises.",
  "In 1994, his father Antonio started the cruise line in Italy with two ships.",
  "Lefebvre took over the company in 2001 and turned it into a luxury cruise line that travels to 900 destinations worldwide.",
  "In June 2018, Lefebvre sold two thirds of the company to Royal Caribbean for $1 billion. He still owns the rest of the company.",
  "In February 2019, Lefebvre bought 85% of the American luxury travel company Abercrombie & Kent for an undisclosed amount."
]